                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">1,245</h3>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="trend-positive text-sm font-semibold">+4.8%</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-2">geçen ay</span>
